{"id":"87ba138e-00ea-4cc0-b30e-382de4987b52","name":"Reinhardt ◦◦ Runaway Duchess","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\">╭⊱⋰⊱╯◦◦╰⊱⋰⊱╮<br><span style=\"color: rgb(213, 188, 133);\">You were already a duchess. You just didn't know it.</span><br>╰⊱⋰⊱╮◦◦╭⊱⋰⊱╯</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>Possessive Duke Char x Noble User ◦◦ FEMPOV ◦◦ Pregnancy ◦◦ One-Night Stand ◦◦ Possessive</em><br>Setting: Medieval | Species: Humans Only</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/dTZ2eA_59rMCwn_j2HXvN.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(213, 188, 133);\">Duke Reinhardt rules Marburg with an iron fist. Cold. Ruthless. Untouchable.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">When he met {{user}} at the capital, it only took one look. One glance, one conversation, and he was captivated. One kiss turned into more, and they spent the night together without hesitation. No protection—why should it matter? He already knew he wasn’t letting her go.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">But... by morning, she was gone. That wasn't supposed to happen.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">He looked for her everywhere, but he couldn't find her. Coming back to his territory empty-handed felt... wrong.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Six months later, he was back in the capital for the Crown Prince’s son’s celebration. And of all the times, he never expected, he saw her again. Just as striking as before—and now, visibly pregnant. With his child, obviously. There's no doubt about it. <span style=\"color: rgb(113, 113, 113);\">There was something else, too. A ring on her finger. Not that it mattered.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(213, 188, 133);\">Reinhardt has found his lost Duchess, and he isn't letting her go.</span></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://rentry.co/reinhardt-von-einhorn\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>👉 <u>REINHARDT'S FULL CHARACTER SHEET</u> 👈</strong></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(96, 96, 96);\"><em>The lorebooks are only visible to me. Please use the character sheet and E.K. carrd website as guides.</em></span></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/0QmQxZ6U-RML-K8da3Iov.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/f26625cf-07bb-4065-96ea-abfc470b6f31_character-karsten-%E2%97%A6%E2%97%A6-annoying-prince\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/qamCP3s1gOeul3fefO5Qm.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></a><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/2ab87fe5-d869-4e89-bf9b-2e5a63794c65_character-wilhelm-%E2%97%A6%E2%97%A6-your-crown-prince\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/1rgg5m2_GCgkVqfCSzjjj.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></a><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/190f3966-0595-4cd4-ab0f-571119f06ea3_character-aldric-%E2%97%A6%E2%97%A6-stoic-knight\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/h7gOgY8NvQ1CITiOMYOax.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></a><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/dcee83d1-ad44-4ff5-99d4-9c13e247c4ff_character-marco-%E2%97%A6%E2%97%A6-fake-engagement\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/ghfmxNA5rM637bIK1jGBA.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></a><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/986c5909-ef6e-4c0a-81ec-3931c6320858_character-alistair-%E2%97%A6%E2%97%A6-lord-commander\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"htt